1
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:35,980
[Zhan Zhao Adventures]

2
00:01:35,980 --> 00:01:37,980
[Episode 2]

3
00:02:08,850 --> 00:02:09,850
You should leave now.

4
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,260
Get as far away as possible.

5
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:13,730
The people from Hanshui Palace

6
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:15,660
weren't seriously injured.

7
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,980
They might come back looking for you.

8
00:02:19,630 --> 00:02:20,850
I may not be able to protect you.

9
00:02:21,150 --> 00:02:21,890
Following me

10
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:23,340
won't be safe.

11
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,100
Since when did Yan Ziqing

12
00:02:26,110 --> 00:02:27,380
become so useless?

13
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:30,730
Are you injured?

14
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,690
It's my own incompetence.

15
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:34,980
Come here.

16
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:38,260
Are the people from Hanshui Palace really that powerful?

17
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:40,660
I

18
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,130
have kept the child here for you.

19
00:02:43,630 --> 00:02:44,100
Come.

20
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:45,500
You didn't drink that poison, right?

21
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,260
That's good, then.

22
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,130
It's getting dark.

23
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:51,660
Take him down the mountain quickly.

24
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:52,980
What about you?

25
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:55,380
Have you forgotten?

26
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,500
We aren't traveling together.

27
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:58,200
We just agreed

28
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,100
that we are even now.

29
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:00,450
I helped you shake off Yan Ziqing,

30
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:01,830
and you drove away the Hanshui Palace people

31
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:02,580
and even saved the child.

32
00:03:02,730 --> 00:03:04,260
Technically, I'm the one who owes you a favor.

33
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:08,850
So this is the Linglong Manor way

34
00:03:09,010 --> 00:03:10,310
of handling favors?

35
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,850
No matter what, I don't like being in debt to anyone.

36
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:17,730
That sound came from the east.

37
00:03:18,470 --> 00:03:19,270
Let's head down the mountain

38
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:19,940
and find a place to hide.

39
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,410
What if we run into them on the way?

40
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,500
The drum signals are telling

41
00:03:22,590 --> 00:03:23,260
the pursuers to climb

42
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,130
from the eastern side.

43
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,610
We'll go down from the west.

44
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,660
You can even understand drum signals?

45
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:28,820
The training routines of official troops

46
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:30,380
are mostly the same.

47
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,940
I only have a surface-level understanding.

48
00:03:32,950 --> 00:03:34,560
Have you offended the government too?

49
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,290
We won't make it down before dark.

50
00:03:43,470 --> 00:03:44,470
Let's find a place to hide first.

51
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:45,260
Let's go.

52
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:14,820
What is being enshrined here?

53
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,610
It looks terrifying.

54
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:21,020
It's a Yaksha.

55
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:28,540
There seemed to be one behind the inn's counter too.

56
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,540
How strange.

57
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,930
Why would anyone worship a demon?

58
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:33,610
In the Xiangzhou region,

59
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,540
many people worship the Yaksha.

60
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,700
It must be a local custom.

61
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,250
Linglong Manor is located in Xiangzhou.

62
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,050
Have you never seen this, Huo?

63
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:51,050
I usually stay within the manor.

64
00:04:51,190 --> 00:04:53,140
I know very little about the world outside.

65
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,050
No wonder.

66
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,220
Even the innkeeper

67
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:00,340
said I looked like an outsider.

68
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,780
Is that wound on your back

69
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:55,660
really alright?

70
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:57,730
It's fine.

71
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,730
Just a flesh wound.

72
00:06:10,910 --> 00:06:12,370
This is our Linglong Manor's

73
00:06:12,370 --> 00:06:13,280
specially made Linglong Honey.

74
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:14,610
It can stop bleeding and relieve pain.

75
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:16,980
Thank you, Huo.

76
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,410
So, tell me.

77
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,660
How did you get into trouble with Yan Ziqing and others?

78
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:36,810
Just some martial arts world grudges.

79
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,580
It's nothing major.

80
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:41,500
Actually,

81
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,490
Linglong Manor has some ties

82
00:06:43,490 --> 00:06:44,700
with the Yunying Sect.

83
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,460
Why don't you tell me about it?

84
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:47,330
Perhaps

85
00:06:47,330 --> 00:06:48,660
I can help mediate for you.

86
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:54,700
What are you laughing at?

87
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,120
Do you think I'm not capable of it?

88
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,510
I simply don't believe

89
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:02,730
you can even return to Linglong Manor.

90
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,690
What do you mean?

91
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,180
You claim

92
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,780
that no one dares to mess with Linglong Manor in Xiangzhou,

93
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,290
yet you'd rather flee with a child

94
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,930
than go back to ask for help.

95
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,170
Doesn't that mean you've caused huge trouble

96
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,660
and can't go back anymore?

97
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,580
It's not that I can't go back.

98
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,220
I just don't want to.

99
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:25,180
The Yinyang An is the greatest treasure

100
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:26,080
of Linglong Manor.

101
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:27,250
It's said

102
00:07:27,290 --> 00:07:29,100
it never leaves the Huo Family Ancestral Hall.

103
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:31,460
Now, this sword

104
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,580
is in your hands,

105
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,660
yet you don't even have any bodyguards

106
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:35,290
accompanying you.

107
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,340
I assume that when you left,

108
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:38,780
Master Huo

109
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,250
wasn't aware of it?

110
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:46,540
Alright.

111
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:47,780
You guessed it.

112
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,540
But I didn't cause any trouble.

113
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:53,140
I just happened to ruin

114
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,140
the marriage between the Huo family and Shao Jizu.

115
00:07:55,950 --> 00:07:57,020
Why did you do that?

116
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:58,460
Because the Huo family's eldest daughter

117
00:07:58,470 --> 00:07:59,850
doesn't want to marry someone she doesn't like.

118
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,040
Everyone says

119
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,810
this Shao Jizu is decent.

120
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:07,410
So what?

121
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:08,600
Does being decent mean you have to get married?

122
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,340
Speaking of decent,

123
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:13,020
our young mistress is decent too.

124
00:08:13,310 --> 00:08:14,780
She's studied literature and martial arts since she was a child.

125
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,260
It's just that our young mistress

126
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:19,090
has never seen

127
00:08:19,090 --> 00:08:20,580
the world outside Linglong Manor.

128
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:26,050
Even if she is to marry,

129
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,480
it has to wait until she

130
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,810
goes out to see the world,

131
00:08:29,810 --> 00:08:30,780
gains some experience,

132
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:31,890
and judges for herself

133
00:08:31,890 --> 00:08:33,460
that this person is truly decent.

134
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:38,610
That makes sense.

135
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,420
However,

136
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,850
to see through someone like Shao Jizu,

137
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,060
you don't need to roam

138
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:45,890
the martial world.

139
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:48,340
I saw through him long ago.

140
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:49,980
He

141
00:08:50,510 --> 00:08:52,120
has an indescribable air of hypocrisy

142
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,890
and arrogance.

143
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:56,420
He usually says my young mistress

144
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:57,650
has great martial arts

145
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,980
and is a martial arts prodigy.

146
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,510
He even says that in time,

147
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:01,420
she will surely defeat him.

148
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,240
Leaving aside whether he means

149
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,450
what he says or not,

150
00:09:04,660 --> 00:09:05,410
just this phrase,

151
00:09:05,410 --> 00:09:06,490
"will surely defeat him,"

152
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:07,460
isn't that arrogant?

153
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:09,890
Why should he be the standard?

154
00:09:10,390 --> 00:09:11,770
It's not like he's some grandmaster.

155
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:13,820
Your young mistress

156
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,180
is quite good at reading people.

157
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:16,220
Of course she is.

158
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,730
It's just a pity that my young mistress

159
00:09:22,730 --> 00:09:24,300
has never defeated Shao Jizu once.

160
00:09:24,810 --> 00:09:25,530
It's so frustrating.

161
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,250
Martial arts

162
00:09:27,340 --> 00:09:28,130
depend on intuition.

163
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:29,950
No one knows

164
00:09:29,950 --> 00:09:31,300
where a person's limit lies.

165
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:36,850
I really didn't expect

166
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:38,980
that while being chased by soldiers,

167
00:09:39,510 --> 00:09:40,220
and carrying a child

168
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:42,060
who could bring trouble at any moment,

169
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,850
you could still be this happy.

170
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:46,460
I've only been out for a few short days,

171
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,010
and I've already fought with Shengyun Manor

172
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:49,300
and the Tang Clan.

173
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:53,820
Perhaps

174
00:09:53,910 --> 00:09:56,010
there will be even more adventures in the future.

175
00:09:58,550 --> 00:09:59,730
Once we reach the capital,

176
00:09:59,870 --> 00:10:01,200
I'll introduce you to a powerful backer,

177
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:01,820
Zhao.

178
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:02,650
With him around,

179
00:10:02,650 --> 00:10:03,730
we have nothing to fear.

180
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,530
Never mind Shengyun Manor

181
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:06,700
or Hanshui Palace,

182
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,420
even if the Southern and Northern Heroes came,

183
00:10:08,420 --> 00:10:09,180
I wouldn't be afraid.

184
00:10:10,510 --> 00:10:11,300
Someone surnamed Zhao

185
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:13,420
who's also your backer...

186
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,580
There is likely only one such person in the capital.

187
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:17,130
That's him.

188
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,240
Lord of Nanqing Palace,

189
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,500
younger cousin of the current Emperor,

190
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:20,300
Zhao Zhuoqing.

191
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:22,700
Huo,

192
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:23,940
you're a friend of King Hui?

193
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:25,490
You know him?

194
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,460
Do you also know

195
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:28,480
the young servant by his side,

196
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,220
Zhao Zhi'er?

197
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:30,980
The one

198
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:33,300
who's known as Deities' Bane?

199
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:36,370
As for Deities' Bane,

200
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:37,730
I'm actually more familiar

201
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:40,250
with the one called Ghosts' Doom.

202
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,770
Ming Zhu'er

203
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,130
from Lord Zhan's household?

204
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,270
I've heard that they

205
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:46,220
are quite the pair of rascals.

206
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,050
The children in Dongjing

207
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,730
have even written nursery rhymes about their exploits.

208
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,370
Have you been pranked by them too?

209
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,980
Not exactly pranked,

210
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:54,940
but they have caused

211
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:57,220
quite a lot of trouble for me.

212
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,370
You've been probing me for information all along.

213
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:03,890
But now,

214
00:11:03,910 --> 00:11:04,820
I've caught you slipping.

215
00:11:07,630 --> 00:11:09,060
You must be someone from the official circles.

216
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,100
Otherwise, you wouldn't know

217
00:11:11,110 --> 00:11:11,940
so many things.

218
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,890
Are you sure the one you met

219
00:11:14,900 --> 00:11:15,820
was his accomplice?

220
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,010
Most likely.

221
00:11:17,430 --> 00:11:18,540
This person had excellent lightness skills.

222
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:19,750
He led me in circles

223
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:20,780
through the forest.

224
00:11:21,060 --> 00:11:21,780
After that,

225
00:11:21,990 --> 00:11:22,930
I completely lost

226
00:11:22,930 --> 00:11:23,600
his trail.

227
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:24,980
That's strange.

228
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:26,700
I've never heard anything

229
00:11:26,710 --> 00:11:27,580
about him having an accomplice.

230
00:11:32,580 --> 00:11:35,200
[Yan Ziqing, Yunying Sect; Mo Dao, Leader of the Xiuluo Cult]

231
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,100
In this season,

232
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,250
there shouldn't be so many fallen leaves.

233
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:51,300
It's the Thousand-Fold Dragon-Slaying Twist from Hanshui Palace.

234
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,460
The one fighting here

235
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,420
shouldn't be him.

236
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,450
He was struck by your "Love at First Sight."

237
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:58,320
He wouldn't be stupid enough to get involved

238
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,060
with Hanshui Palace again.

239
00:11:59,890 --> 00:12:00,430
No.

240
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:02,330
It's certainly him.

241
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,300
In this world,

242
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:05,850
how many others

243
00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:08,220
can withstand the Thousand-Fold Dragon-Slaying Twist?

244
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:09,570
We must

245
00:12:09,570 --> 00:12:11,220
capture him before Shao Jizu does.

246
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,420
We can't let this massive credit

247
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,730
slip through our fingers.

248
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,010
He's severely injured,

249
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:22,300
yet he can still block a blow from the Sun Envoy.

250
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,890
You and I

251
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:25,770
are no match for him.

252
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,010
Do you know why

253
00:12:29,010 --> 00:12:30,100
the Yunying Sect never

254
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:30,610
makes it big?

255
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,890
Too many annoying rules.

256
00:12:33,390 --> 00:12:34,180
Who says capturing someone

257
00:12:34,220 --> 00:12:35,010
requires brute force?

258
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,060
Stupid.

259
00:12:36,270 --> 00:12:38,060
When the Xiuluo Cult roams the martial world,

260
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,370
it's not martial arts we rely on.

261
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:40,940
If we want to catch him,

262
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,100
there are plenty of ways.

263
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:44,490
What?

264
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:45,940
Stopping the search?

265
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:46,850
Search for what?

266
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:48,730
If he wants to leave Xiangzhou,

267
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,060
he has to take the waterways.

268
00:12:50,300 --> 00:12:51,790
We'll just wait for him at the ferry.

269
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,180
Waiting at our ease

270
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,710
is much easier

271
00:12:54,710 --> 00:12:55,680
than exhausting ourselves

272
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:56,370
searching these mountains.

273
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:21,370
I wonder who could have been so cruel.

274
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:24,700
Huo,

275
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:26,820
this child

276
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:28,100
should be from Hanshui Palace.

277
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:30,980
When you went to lure Yan Ziqing away,

278
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:32,030
the Sun Envoy mentioned

279
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,650
he hadn't taken his medicine for some days.

280
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,370
Come to think of it,

281
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:38,220
he's been drinking poison there since childhood.

282
00:13:38,690 --> 00:13:39,850
Drinking poison since childhood?

283
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,250
Drinking poison since childhood,

284
00:13:45,250 --> 00:13:46,420
yet he's perfectly fine now.

285
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,420
You mean,

286
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:51,430
like the people

287
00:13:51,430 --> 00:13:52,530
from the Xiuluo Cult and Tang Clan,

288
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,630
