291
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,820
Do you remember Ge Yunfei?

292
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,590
He didn't want to kill this child,

293
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:04,010
but rather use him

294
00:14:04,390 --> 00:14:05,010
to save a life.

295
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:05,690
Save a life?

296
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,010
Huo, you must have heard of

297
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,010
Hanshui Palace's secret treasure,

298
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,130
the Changhong Jade?

299
00:14:12,350 --> 00:14:13,600
In the century-old Hanshui Palace,

300
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:15,240
there is the rare Changhong Jade.

301
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:17,330
[Changhong Jade, Hanshui Palace]
Nurtured by the Azure Three-Lives Water,

302
00:14:17,330 --> 00:14:18,650
this jade is precious

303
00:14:18,790 --> 00:14:20,450
