304
00:14:20,670 --> 00:14:21,720
The treasure Shengyun Manor

305
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,610
and the Tang Clan are fighting over

306
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,220
is not an object,

307
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,420
but this child.

308
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,700
The Changhong Jade isn't a piece of jade

309
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:29,730
