312
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,300
likely came from this.

313
00:14:40,390 --> 00:14:41,300
No wonder.

314
00:14:41,590 --> 00:14:43,090
There is always a faint

315
00:14:43,090 --> 00:14:44,340
