327
00:15:08,860 --> 00:15:10,060
kept by Hanshui Palace.

328
00:15:11,330 --> 00:15:12,180
But

329
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:13,870
rumors of the Changhong Jade in the martial world

330
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:14,700
have existed for over a century.

331
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:16,770
Could this child

332
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,580
really be a hundred years old?

333
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:20,460
Don't all the eldest daughters of Linglong Manor

334
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:21,710
take on

335
00:15:21,710 --> 00:15:23,250
