345
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:42,790
Wandering the world at such a young age,

346
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:45,770
with everyone coveting his extraordinary powers,

347
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:48,100
it's not surprising

348
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:49,980
