371
00:16:38,490 --> 00:16:39,440
Do you still intend

372
00:16:39,570 --> 00:16:40,770
to continue protecting him?

373
00:16:49,420 --> 00:16:50,940
If we are right

374
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:53,420
that he has grown up in Hanshui Palace since he was small,

375
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:55,750
