515
00:28:00,980 --> 00:28:02,380
[Liu Yan, Five Poisons of the Xiuluo Cult]

516
00:28:02,380 --> 00:28:03,860
[Gui Mu, Five Poisons of the Xiuluo Cult]

517
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:08,260
[Mei Ying and Han Feng, Five Poisons of the Xiuluo Cult]

518
00:28:13,310 --> 00:28:14,770
Now that you've been hit by my "Love at First Sight,"

519
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:17,530
