569
00:34:24,590 --> 00:34:25,490
he didn't drink your blood?

570
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:33,490
You're the one who made the move

571
00:35:33,590 --> 00:35:34,570
at the inn, right?

572
00:35:35,840 --> 00:35:37,010
Heavily wounded,

573
00:35:37,110 --> 00:35:38,650
yet still meddling in others' business?

574
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,460
Thirty years ago,

575
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:43,170
the old Master of Shengyun Manor

576
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:45,090
died at the hands of the Tang Clan.

577
00:35:45,960 --> 00:35:46,530
Since then,

578
00:35:47,510 --> 00:35:49,090
you have held a bitter grudge.

579
00:35:50,190 --> 00:35:51,440
Your sect excels in swordplay,

580
00:35:51,710 --> 00:35:53,530
but unfortunately, the Tang Clan is expert in poisons.

581
00:35:53,750 --> 00:35:55,130
You've clashed several times

582
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:58,050
but never gained any advantage.

583
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:00,300
So,

584
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:03,650
when you heard of the Hanshui Palace secret treasure,

585
00:36:04,550 --> 00:36:06,740
you were determined to seize it at any cost.

586
00:36:09,590 --> 00:36:10,530
Shengyun Manor

587
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:12,650
has already lost two Masters.

588
00:36:14,070 --> 00:36:14,780
Master Jiao,

589
00:36:14,880 --> 00:36:16,260
don't remain stubborn.

590
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:28,490
Didn't you say my skills were decent?

591
00:36:28,590 --> 00:36:29,490
I'll hold them off for a while.

592
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:30,800
It's a good chance to see

593
00:36:30,800 --> 00:36:31,900
if what you said is true.

594
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,780
Master Jiao, you arrived quite quickly.

595
00:36:35,630 --> 00:36:36,690
It seems you're willing to risk

596
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:37,980
offending both Linglong Manor

597
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:39,530
and Hanshui Palace

598
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:42,260
just to take Changhong Jade.

599
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:43,900
I

600
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:45,740
do indeed have to

601
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,420
show some respect to Hanshui Palace.

602
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:49,300
But Linglong Manor?

603
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:51,460
I don't care about them at all.

604
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:22,530
The Bronze Sword?

605
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:24,300
Yinyang An

606
00:37:24,440 --> 00:37:25,980
can overcome any weapon in the world.

607
00:37:26,230 --> 00:37:28,780
That's because when it was forged,

608
00:37:28,960 --> 00:37:30,260
lodestone was added.

609
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:31,570
Therefore,

610
00:37:31,670 --> 00:37:33,320
in the face of bronze weapons,

611
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,820
it is just an ordinary sword.

612
00:37:36,240 --> 00:37:37,070
How did you know

613
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:38,070
the secret of Yinyang An?

614
00:37:39,150 --> 00:37:41,070
I know many more secrets

615
00:37:41,070 --> 00:37:42,610
of your Huo family's martial arts.

616
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:34,010
Even if you risk your life,

617
00:38:34,230 --> 00:38:35,650
you won't be able to protect this child.

618
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:37,260
After I've finished him off,

619
00:38:38,150 --> 00:38:39,490
I'll come back to deal with you!

620
00:39:18,440 --> 00:39:19,260
Save him.

621
00:39:19,510 --> 00:39:20,260
Save him now!

622
00:39:41,030 --> 00:39:42,490
You've actually studied the "Glimpse of Beauty?"

623
00:39:45,110 --> 00:39:46,400
The one they want is me.

624
00:39:46,400 --> 00:39:47,440
You two should leave now.

625
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:53,210
I am not going to leave you behind.

626
00:39:58,920 --> 00:40:00,380
Even if we must fight to the death today,

627
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:02,250
we cannot leave this threat behind

628
00:40:02,250 --> 00:40:03,090
for Linglong Manor.

629
00:40:36,950 --> 00:40:37,630
What?

630
00:40:38,070 --> 00:40:39,210
Haven't you had enough yet?

631
00:40:39,710 --> 00:40:40,990
To tell you the truth,

632
00:40:41,210 --> 00:40:42,490
this sword formation

633
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:44,980
was created specifically to counter your Huo family.

634
00:40:45,050 --> 00:40:46,570
You won't be able to break it.

635
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:49,940
Why haven't you saved him yet?

636
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:51,490
Save him!

637
00:41:54,110 --> 00:41:54,860
Who told you

638
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:56,900
about the secret of Yinyang An

639
00:41:56,900 --> 00:41:57,980
and "Glimpse of Beauty?"

640
00:41:58,760 --> 00:42:00,240
And where did this sword formation come from?

641
00:42:01,110 --> 00:42:02,650
We have no grievances with Shengyun Manor.

642
00:42:03,320 --> 00:42:04,420
Why have you gone to such lengths

643
00:42:04,420 --> 00:42:05,150
to target us like this?

644
00:42:06,860 --> 00:42:08,150
If you want to know,

645
00:42:08,710 --> 00:42:10,350
go ask Huo Tianxing yourself.

646
00:42:11,150 --> 00:42:12,210
However,

647
00:42:12,480 --> 00:42:14,160
even if you let me go today,

648
00:42:14,160 --> 00:42:15,380
I won't be grateful.

649
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:16,390
One day,

650
00:42:17,670 --> 00:42:19,050
you will certainly regret this.

651
00:42:19,510 --> 00:42:21,130
The sword formation you spent so much effort studying

652
00:42:21,230 --> 00:42:22,260
was broken by me in an instant.

653
00:42:22,440 --> 00:42:22,980
What do I have to fear?

654
00:42:25,030 --> 00:42:26,740
Even if you go back and study a few more,

655
00:42:27,030 --> 00:42:27,570
I still won't be afraid.

656
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:33,490
Wait a moment.

657
00:42:35,110 --> 00:42:35,610
What?

658
00:42:36,550 --> 00:42:37,420
Are you regretting it already?

659
00:42:39,110 --> 00:42:40,460
Have your disciples double up.

660
00:42:40,710 --> 00:42:41,490
Leave two horses for us.

661
00:43:30,860 --> 00:43:36,340
♪In this martial world, true friends are rare♪

662
00:43:37,020 --> 00:43:41,740
♪Yet some would fight by my side♪

663
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:43,900
♪Across towering mountains♪

664
00:43:43,940 --> 00:43:48,940
♪Risking all for peace beneath the heavens♪

665
00:43:49,820 --> 00:43:56,220
♪If we face life and death together, why fear the hard road ahead?♪

666
00:43:56,300 --> 00:44:02,780
♪Roaming this endless martial road♪

667
00:44:02,940 --> 00:44:09,180
♪Seeing the world's joy and sorrow pass by♪

668
00:44:09,380 --> 00:44:12,420
♪Honor still burns within us♪

669
00:44:12,540 --> 00:44:18,620
♪Still, love and grudges are the hardest to escape♪

670
00:44:18,860 --> 00:44:23,300
♪Too tangled to let go♪

671
00:44:24,820 --> 00:44:29,060
♪Who says loyalty and honor can't coexist?♪

672
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:32,740
♪One swing of the sword ends it all♪

673
00:44:33,060 --> 00:44:38,660
♪My heart stays true, just as before♪

674
00:44:39,260 --> 00:44:44,380
♪Right and wrong will reveal themselves♪

675
00:44:44,740 --> 00:44:49,620
♪Why let others decide for us?♪

676
00:44:49,860 --> 00:44:54,060
♪If this journey has no way back♪

677
00:44:54,260 --> 00:44:57,660
♪Then there's no need for sorrow♪

678
00:44:58,460 --> 00:45:04,420
♪Let a lone boat carry me past the mountains♪

679
00:45:04,860 --> 00:45:10,100
♪One last glance, and the clouds are gone♪

680
00:45:10,100 --> 00:45:15,700
♪The bright moon will light my way home♪

681
00:45:16,380 --> 00:45:23,180
♪The bright moon will light my way home♪
